Google search in sublime text 2.

INSTALL:
You may install this via "Package Control" 
http://wbond.net/sublime_packages/package_control



USAGE:

Search selected text
* Select text
* Right click on it and click "search selection"
* See results on native popup menu
* Press enter to open in browser
 
Search user's input
* Press Ctrl+Shift+g (Cmd+Shift+g on Mac OS X)
* See results on native popup menu
* Press enter to open in browser
